Reads in any classes from the "dizzy_content.css" file:
.red {
  color: red;
}

.green {
  color: green;
}

.absolute {
  position: absolute;
}

.underline {
  border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
}


Works with any textarea given the class "dizzywyg"

<body>
  <div style="width:600px;">
    <h1>The Dizzywyg is upon us.</h1>
    <p>You may or may not have known.</p>

		<textarea class="dizzywyg"></textarea>
  </div>
</body>
